pre process

tpm <- function(counts, lengths) {
  rpk <- counts / lengths
  coef <- sum(rpk) / 1e6
  rpk/coef
}

rownames(all_data)=make.unique(all_data$gene_name)
lengths = all_data[,5]
omitgenes= startsWith(rownames(all_data),"ERCC-")
all_data=all_data[!omitgenes,]
all_data=all_data[,7:ncol(all_data)]


cell.labels <- gsub(".gene_counts.tsv","",colnames(all_data))
cell.labels <- gsub(".sort.bam","",cell.labels)
cell.labels <- gsub("_",".",cell.labels)
cell.labels <- gsub(".S[0-9]*","",cell.labels)
well=regmatches(cell.labels, regexpr("[A-H][0-9]*$", cell.labels))
plate=substr(cell.labels,1,nchar(cell.labels)-nchar(well)-1)

colnames(all_data)=paste(plate,well,sep="_")
